# Frontend Rules

React + TypeScript + Tailwind + Vite dashboard.

## Scope
- App shell, routing, dashboards
- Profile, document, preference, policy forms
- Workflow and application monitoring UI
- Artifacts and notification displays

## Do NOT
- Implement backend business logic in frontend
- Use giant global state

## Conventions
- Feature folders aligned with backend domains
- TanStack Query for data
- Typed API client matching backend contracts
- Reusable components (status badge, metric card, table, empty/loading states)
